"color=\"%2\">%title%</font>,                           <font color=\"%3\">"
"%artist%</font>, <font color=\"%4\">%composer%</"
"font>,                           <font color=\"%5\">%year%</font>, <font "
"color=\"%6\">%album%</font>,                           <font color=\"%7\">"
"%albumartist%</font>, <font color=\"%8\">%comment%</"
"font>,                           <font color=\"%9\">%genre%</font>, %ignore%."
msgstr ""
"ໂທເຄັນຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ສາມາດໃຊ້ເພື່ອອະທິບາຍໂຄງສ້າງຊື່ຟາຍ:<br>                           <font "
"color=\"%1\">%track%</font>, <font color=\"%2\">%title%</"
"font>,                           <font color=\"%3\">%artist%</font>, <font "
"color=\"%4\">%composer%</font>,                           <font color=\"%5\">"
"%year%</font>, <font color=\"%6\">%album%</font>,                           "
"<font color=\"%7\">%albumartist%</font>, <font color=\"%8\">%comment%</"
"font>,                           <font color=\"%9\">%genre%</font>, %ignore%."

