msgstr "ຄ້າຍຄືກັບສິລະປິນໃດກໍຕາມໃນລາຍການເພງປະຈຸບັນ (ຕາມທີ່ລາຍງານໂດຍ EchoNest)"

#: dynamic/biases/EchoNestBias.cpp:142
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<a href=\"http://the.echonest.com/\">the echonest</a> thinks the artist is "
